reviewText: Cool to see how things that some people may have found no value are very valuable and how some people think something is very valuable and it worth nothing.

I used to be able to watch this for free, now they want you to purchase each episode.
1 star!
Amazing,amusing, interesting, surprising, entertaining , captivating . Worth watching. Always something old and new to the viewer. Would recommend to the careful client.

Really fun to see everyone's treasures, and to hear the stories about how they acquired them. The best part of the show is when people who pulled something out of the garbage discover that it's worth thousands!
This was a birthday present for a relative that enjoys "junking" or the art of recognizing the value of an item.
